---
// src/components/Testimonials.astro
---
<section id="testimonios" class="py-24 bg-white border-t border-slate-100 relative overflow-hidden scroll-mt-24">
  
  <div class="absolute inset-0 -z-10 overflow-hidden pointer-events-none opacity-30">
    <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-[500px] h-[500px] bg-blue-500/5 rounded-full blur-[100px]"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-20 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 tracking-tight mb-6">
        Confianza que <br class="md:hidden" />
        <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-700 via-blue-600 to-cyan-500">
          Cruza Fronteras.
        </span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-slate-500 font-medium text-balance">
        Empresas HVAC-R en toda América ya ordenaron su operación con Lissi.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-3">
       <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-sm border border-slate-100 relative hover:-translate-y-1 transition-transform duration-300">
        <div class="text-6xl text-blue-100 absolute -top-4 left-6 font-serif">“</div>
        <p class="text-slate-700 mb-8 relative z-10 leading-relaxed font-medium">
          Lissi nos permitió estandarizar nuestros reportes técnicos. Ahora la información fluye desde terreno a la oficina sin perder ni un dato.
        </p>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 border-t border-slate-200/60 pt-6">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-600 to-blue-800 flex items-center justify-center text-white text-lg font-bold shadow-lg shadow-blue-500/20">
            AG
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="font-bold text-slate-900 flex items-center gap-2">
              Andrés Gutiérrez
              <img src="https://flagcdn.com/24x18/co.png" width="24" height="18" alt="Colombia">
            </div>
            <div class="text-xs font-bold text-blue-600 uppercase tracking-wider mb-0.5">Eolis</div>
            <div class="text-xs text-slate-400">Bogotá, Colombia</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-sm border border-slate-100 relative hover:-translate-y-1 transition-transform duration-300">
        <div class="text-6xl text-blue-100 absolute -top-4 left-6 font-serif">“</div>
        <p class="text-slate-700 mb-8 relative z-10 leading-relaxed font-medium">
          Manejar la refrigeración comercial requiere precisión. Lissi nos dio el control de activos que necesitábamos para escalar en Miami.
        </p>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 border-t border-slate-200/60 pt-6">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-600 to-blue-800 flex items-center justify-center text-white text-lg font-bold shadow-lg shadow-blue-500/20">
            PC
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="font-bold text-slate-900 flex items-center gap-2">
              Pepe
              <img src="https://flagcdn.com/24x18/us.png" width="24" height="18" alt="USA">
            </div>
            <div class="text-xs font-bold text-blue-600 uppercase tracking-wider mb-0.5">Chill Factor Ref.</div>
            <div class="text-xs text-slate-400">Miami, EE.UU.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-sm border border-slate-100 relative hover:-translate-y-1 transition-transform duration-300">
        <div class="text-6xl text-blue-100 absolute -top-4 left-6 font-serif">“</div>
        <p class="text-slate-700 mb-8 relative z-10 leading-relaxed font-medium">
          Desde que usamos Lissi, los técnicos saben exactamente qué hacer y el cliente recibe su informe al instante. Un cambio total.
        </p>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 border-t border-slate-200/60 pt-6">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-600 to-blue-800 flex items-center justify-center text-white text-lg font-bold shadow-lg shadow-blue-500/20">
            PP
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="font-bold text-slate-900 flex items-center gap-2">
              Pedro Pica
              <img src="https://flagcdn.com/24x18/cl.png" width="24" height="18" alt="Chile">
            </div>
            <div class="text-xs font-bold text-blue-600 uppercase tracking-wider mb-0.5">Cuvolt</div>
            <div class="text-xs text-slate-400">Santiago, Chile</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>